    public class SSLSessionCacheStatistic
extends java.util.HashMap
    Maintains statistic data about the SSL session cache behavior of a simulated load test user.
    See Also:
    PerformanceData.getSSLCacheEfficiency(), PerformanceData.getSSLSessionCreateCount(), PerformanceData.getSSLSessionReuseCount(), Serialized Form
